This is the change file for atangle.aweb.  Here I change the
default output from ".a" files to ".adb" and ".ads" files.
This is necessary for GNAT.

@x
The ``banner line'' defined here should be changed whenever \.{ATANGLE} is
modified.
 
@d banner=="This is ATANGLE, Version 1.0"
@y
The ``banner line'' defined here should be changed whenever \.{ATANGLE} is
modified.
 
@d banner=="This is ATANGLE, Version 1.1 (NRaD Version)"
@z


